      "source_repo": "adelarsq/vim-emoji-icon-theme",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Emoji/Unicode Icons Theme for Vim and Neovim with support for 40+ plugins and 380+ filetypes \ud83c\udfa8\ud83d\udc99\ud83d\udc9b\ud83e\udd0d\ud83d\udc9a"
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "adelarsq/vim-emoji-icon-theme",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "This plugin uses emojis to represent filetypes, signs and symbols for many plugins. So there is no need for overrided fonts."
    },
    {
      "source_kind": "repo-description",
      "source_repo": "adelarsq/neoline.vim",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Status Line for Neovim focused on beauty and performance \u2705\ud83d\udc99\ud83d\udc9b\ud83e\udd0d\ud83d\udc9a"
